</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[86,1072,570,604]" pageId="182" pageNumber="785" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="182.[86,1292,294,761]" box="[86,1072,570,604]" pageId="182" pageNumber="785">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[86,321,570,604]" pageId="182" pageNumber="785">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Large-eared Field Mice are nocturnal and terrestrial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[88,1027,614,643]" pageId="182" pageNumber="785" type="biology_ecology">
